# TradeTracker & Affiliate Links

Affiliate offers come from TradeTracker XML product feeds.

## Data strategy

- **Phase A (current):** fetch + parse feeds server-side with Next.js `fetch` caching / ISR
  (`revalidate`). **No database.** Keep fetching in server components / server code only.
- **Phase B (future, tracked in Linear):** scheduled sync into a database (Prisma/Postgres)
  for richer search/filtering. Don't build this until that ticket is picked up.
- Always normalize raw feed shapes into the internal `TravelOffer` model before it reaches
  the UI. Per-advertiser mapping lives in `mapToOffers`.

## Affiliate integrity

- Outbound affiliate links use `rel="sponsored nofollow"` and open per UX spec.
- Every page/section with affiliate links MUST show a clear affiliate disclosure (legal
  requirement). Never hide the commercial relationship.
- Feed URLs/credentials come from env (`TRADETRACKER_FEED_URLS`); never commit them.
